		"description": "<p>At 6th level, your connection to dragonkind manifests itself by taking on some of a dragon&rsquo;s hoarding instinct. You can attune to an additional magic item, and the process of attuning to a magical item is quicker for you, taking only 10 minutes rather than an hour. In addition, as long as you have a container capable of holding them, you treat any coins or gems you carry as having no weight at all. Finally, if you can sleep on top of a pile of coins and gems with a combined value equal to 1000 x your proficiency bonus, you can treat a long rest as having taken place in a haven, even if it normally would not. Once you have rested this way, you can&rsquo;t do so again for a week.</p>",
